        'Long division practice using base-ten blocks → partial quotients → standard algorithm',
        'Fraction kit unit: paper strips, fraction bars, number lines (CRITICAL — iReady does NOT report fractions)',
        'CRA progression for decimals: base-ten blocks → grids → symbolic notation',
