        'MA.4.FR.1–2 — Fraction equivalence, comparison, +/–, multiplying fraction × whole number (ALL Tier 2 students)',
        'MA.4.AR.1.1–1.3 — Multi-step word problems with whole numbers and fractions',
        'MA.4.M.1.1–1.2 — Measurement conversions (ft↔in, m↔cm, kg↔g)',
