        'FAST-formatted practice problems 2x/week — focus on multi-step word problems and fraction comparison',
        'Fact fluency check-in weekly — goal of sub-3-second recall on 0–10 multiplication facts',
        'Fraction unit review with fraction bars and number lines — do NOT skip even for borderline students',
        'Error-analysis routine: students explain WHY a wrong answer is wrong using math vocabulary',
        'Decimal place value visualization: meter sticks, decimal grids, money',
        'Protractor practice 2x/week — measure and sketch angles to nearest 5°',
        'iReady: maintain 45+ min/week; use teacher dashboard to monitor lesson completion',
        'Growth goal conferences: review % progress to typical growth target weekly'
      ],
      resources: ['iReady assigned lessons (Groupings 3–4)','Ready Math Grade 4 toolkit','Math Playground / Prodigy','FAST sample items (FLDOE)','Number line and fraction bar printables','Khan Academy fractions/multiplication/division modules','Physical protractors']
    },
    {
